text: Oodnadatta is a town and locality in South Australia. Oodnadatta may also refer to: ==South Australia== *Oodnadatta (biogeographic subregion), a subregion of the Stony Plains bioregion *Oodnadatta Aboriginal School, an Aboriginal school *Oodnadatta Airport *Oodnadatta Track, a road *Oodnadatta railway station, a heritage listed railway station in Oodnadatta ==Elsewhere== *Oodnadatta, a crater on Mars ==See also== *Coober Pedy Oodnadatta One Day Mail Run
